data.description: Back on the market due to no fault of the seller.  Excellent opportunity to have a beautiful home near downtown Woodstock!!   In sought after Farmington subdivision; Home has newer renovated kitchen with granite counters; Also the master bath has been renovated with granite tops and a gorgeous tile shower.   Kitchen level garage offers a quick entry into the main floor of the home.   Gorgeous fireside family room; Home does have a full separate dining room;  Full basement has been partially finished and has walk out right to the backyard.  Definitely a must see!!
